{"tid":2307995,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"香港外國記者會主席提前離任返美 調職紐約","createTime":"2020-12-01T14:09:52.000Z","updateTime":"2020-12-01T17:48:32.000Z","uid":240362,"like":12,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"9c87baba2b9e3fddb9a9fa83d102f58de42be298","tid":2307995,"uid":240362,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-01T14:09:52.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/Li0r86q11VA5hVowUmtzS2hXpEY=/802x506/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/DPLJ76BO3EGZGS5YP2EXSILBOU.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2FLi0r86q11VA5hVowUmtzS2hXpEY%3D%2F802x506%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FDPLJ76BO3EGZGS5YP2EXSILBOU.jpg&h=167d989a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\nFCC主席Jodi Schneider（前），去年9月18日聯同其他傳媒工作者，舉起標語默站，抗議警方於反送中示威期間，多加阻撓傳媒工作者採訪，甚至使用暴力對待記者。資料圖片<br />\n<br />\n香港外國記者會（FCC）主席、彭博資深國際編輯Jodi Schneider今日公佈，因將調職往紐約及家庭因素，將會於本月底提前離任主席一職返美。有報道指，是次提前離任與本港局勢無關。<br />\n<br />\nJodi Schneider於FCC網站向會員發公開信，稱本月底將會提前離任及離開香港，往紐約任彭博高級編輯，處理美國應對疫情及疫苗相關報道。她指，擔任FCC主席的18個月，以及過往擔任理事時，是其職業生涯的重要時刻，稱十分重視FCC肩負新聞自由的責任，雖然希望完成任期，但須顧及職業發展。<br />\n<br />\n她又指，家庭因素亦是其提早離任的原因之一，因疫情期間難以回美，不希望太過遠離其母親及兒子。<br />\n<br />\n《眾新聞》引述消息指，Schneider離任純屬個人原因，與本港局勢無關。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20201201/242UFF52ONA6XG3NI5JWQDCIGA/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20201201%2F242UFF52ONA6XG3NI5JWQDCIGA%2F&d=3wrM%2FJom4zLweqSprMIx0pa0YVntLK4LebkCjpCDSOM%3D&h=ced15709\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20201201%2F242UFF52ONA6XG3NI5JWQDCIGA%2F&h=713a6da6\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20201201/242UFF52ONA6XG3NI5JWQDCIGA/</a>"},{"pid":"bdce53f00d09550665d15f42d0d57d297bacf11b","tid":2307995,"uid":51346,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime"